The Python companion covers the full 5-step pipeline from the main recipe:[0m[0m
[0m[0m
1. [1mClassify message intent[22m - keyword matching to determine what the patient is asking about (refill, appointment, test result, symptom, billing, or general)[0m[0m
2. [1mGather patient context[22m - targeted retrieval of relevant EHR data based on intent (mock data in this example, with notes on real FHIR integration)[0m[0m
