[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    1553[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;192;197;206m|[38;2;192;197;206m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mProduction-ready (one scenario)[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;192;197;206m [38;2;192;197;206m|[38;2;192;197;206m 52-78 weeks [38;2;192;197;206m|[38;2;192;197;206m Full modality ingestion with cleared imaging AI integration where applicable. ECG interpretation with optional foundation model output. Robust FHIR integration with the target EHR. Comprehensive validation (citation, verbatim quantity, graded term, cross-modality consistency, scope). SMART on FHIR or CDS Hooks integration. Alert-fatigue-aware tiering. Clinical validation studies with domain experts. Clinician feedback pipeline with clinical reviewer triage. Documented regulatory posture, FDA exemption or device path. Operational dashboards and audit trail. Subgroup performance monitoring. [38;2;192;197;206m|[K
